One, two, three,

566
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:47,720
four, five, six.

567
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:48,560
Seven…

568
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:50,080
And a one?

569
00:28:50,360 --> 00:28:52,440
3-37?

