He never loses.

592
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:37,360
He's capable of anything.

593
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,920
Now, now, Mr. Chi.

594
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:11,440
God of Earth,

595
00:31:12,280 --> 00:31:14,320
