596
00:31:15,040 --> 00:31:18,600
The Eastern Capital is my turf.

597
00:31:19,360 --> 00:31:22,440
Those three women embarrassed me here.

598
00:31:22,840 --> 00:31:25,720
I'll be a laughingstock.

599
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:29,000
