00:34:33,560 --> 00:34:34,840
I need to talk to her.

646
00:34:37,710 --> 00:34:38,480
No, no.

647
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:39,760
She needs some time alone.

648
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:40,710
Sit down.

649
00:34:43,520 --> 00:34:44,710
Here, keep drinking.

